OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FHolyrood has passed an historic bill
OL,7,Fwhich could legalise assisted dying in
OL,8,FScotland.
OL,10,FSeventy MSPs backed the Assisted Dying
OL,11,Ffor Terminally Ill Adults (Scotland)
OL,12,FBill, allowing it to progress to the
OL,13,Fnext stage in the parliamentary
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,16,FFifty-six MSPs voted against, while
OL,17,Fone abstained.
OL,19,FAs the vote passed, campaigners
OL,20,Fcheered from the gallery.
