OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MSP Liam McArthur,
OL,7,Fwho is piloting the bill, wept in the
OL,8,Fchamber as he urged others to back the
OL,9,Flegislation which would allow
OL,10,Fterminally ill people deemed mentally
OL,11,Fcapable to choose to end their own
OL,12,Flives.
OL,14,FHe said: "We can't continue to leave
OL,15,Fthis in the most vulnerable box, that
OL,16,Fwould be unforgivable."
OL,18,FPoliticians from all parties shared
OL,19,Femotional personal reasons for their
OL,20,Fdecisions.
