OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth,
OL,7,FScottish Labour, said he backed the
OL,8,Fgeneral principles of the bill.
OL,10,FHe said: "When a constituent looks you
OL,11,Fin the eye and says: 'I'm dying, when
OL,12,Fthat time comes I want the right to
OL,13,Fchoose how I pass in my final days
OL,14,Fwith dignity.' It's hard to respond,
OL,15,F'that's not your decision, that's
OL,16,Fmine.'
OL,18,F"This bill will not mean more people
OL,19,Fwill die but if we can get it right,
OL,20,Fit will mean that fewer people will
OL,21,Fsuffer."
