OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1747337928
OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,F"The extent of internalised coercion,
OL,7,Fthe risk that we choose to die and the
OL,8,Fstate will help is real with this
OL,9,Fbill. The systemic coercion that makes
OL,10,Fus consider for just a moment that
OL,11,Fwe'd be better off dead."
OL,13,FOutside the Scottish Parliament,
OL,14,Fcampaigners both for and against the
OL,15,Fmove held demonstrations.
OL,17,FRetired GP John Macdonald, from
OL,18,FWigtown, has prostate cancer. He is
OL,19,Fnot terminally ill, but supports the
OL,20,Fprinciple of assisted dying.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
