OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FHe said: "I think people should have
OL,7,Fautonomy over how and where and when
OL,8,Fthey wish to die just as they have
OL,9,Fautonomy over every other aspect of
OL,10,Ftheir lives.
OL,12,F"I've had a cancer diagnosis myself,
OL,13,Fand ultimately, in the future, if I
OL,14,Fwas faced with symptoms that I could
OL,15,Fnot cope with I would like to have the
OL,16,Fautonomy to decide for myself that
OL,17,Fenough was enough and to do something
OL,18,Fabout it."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUzD@JO]
