OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FDumfries Pastor Mark Smith opposes the
OL,7,Fproposed legislation and wants to see
OL,8,Fbetter palliative care.
OL,10,FHe said: "The problem is that you're
OL,11,Factually saying the NHS has a license
OL,12,Fto kill and that's what it really
OL,13,Fcomes down to. If this bill was to
OL,14,Fbecome law then it almost puts medical
OL,15,Fprofessionals in the place of playing
OL,16,FGod and I think that's very dangerous."
OL,18,FMark's father died 18 months ago, at
OL,19,Fthe age of 98. He says he may have
OL,20,Ffelt pressured to choose an assisted
OL,21,Fdeath, had it been an option.
OL,26,@rD@JOUxD@gO]
