OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,F"He had a lot of help from the NHS, he
OL,7,Fwent through bowel cancer and they
OL,8,Fsuccessfully operated.
OL,10,F"Had he been under even the inference
OL,11,Fof a pressure, he may well have taken
OL,12,Fthat decision and that would have been
OL,13,Fsuch a shame for me and my siblings,
OL,14,Fwe would have missed out on these
OL,15,Fprecious years with him in his later
OL,16,Flife."
OL,18,FAssisted Dying for Terminally Ill
OL,19,FAdults (Scotland) Bill
