OL,6,FTo be eligible for an assisted death
OL,7,Funder this proposed legislation you
OL,8,Fneed to meet the following criteria:
OL,10,FTwo doctors must be sure that you are
OL,11,Feligible and not being pressured or
OL,12,Fcoerced.
OL,14,FAfter they have agreed, there is a 14
OL,15,Fday reflection period, then you will
OL,16,Fbe given an approved substance that
OL,17,Fyou can choose to take yourself to end
OL,18,Fyour life.
OL,20,FAnalysis by Kieran Andrews, Political
OL,21,FEditor
