OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FIn the 26 years of the Scottish
OL,7,Fparliament, this has the potential to
OL,8,Fbe amongst Holyrood's most significant
OL,9,Fmoments.
OL,11,FBy the tightest of margins, MSPs have
OL,12,Fvoted to back the principles of a bill
OL,13,Fthat would legalise assisted dying.
OL,15,FNow, these are early days and there is
OL,16,Fno guarantee that this will go on to
OL,17,Fbecome law.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
