OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1747337928
OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FYou only needed to listen to the
OL,7,Fcontributions of South Scotland MSPs
OL,8,FColin Smyth, Brian Whittle and Emma
OL,9,FHarper during this evening's debate to
OL,10,Fsee that.
OL,12,FMajor concerns remain about vulnerable
OL,13,Fpeople being coerced into an early
OL,14,Fdeath, the prospect of an expansion
OL,15,Fbeyond the current parameters of the
OL,16,Flegislation happening with limited
OL,17,Foversight and even the fact that
OL,18,FHolyrood does not have all the powers
OL,19,Fto enact this without support from
OL,20,FWestminster.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/14
