OL,3,CMSPs back Assisted Dying Bill at stage
OL,4,Cone
OL,6,FIt is entirely possible that the
OL,7,Fsupport displayed tonight will melt
OL,8,Faway as the parliamentary process
OL,9,Fcontinues in the coming weeks and
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FBut whatever the outcome, a bright
OL,13,Fspot has come from the way the debate
OL,14,Fhas been carried out.
OL,16,FLiam McArthur is a well-respected MSP,
OL,17,Fwho has thought through his arguments
OL,18,Fas he drafted then lobbied for his
OL,19,Fbill.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
